---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | ILAI Academy" description="About Dr. MTD Lakshan and ILAI Academy.">
	<SiteHeader currentPath="/about" />

	<main class="container page">
		<section class="hero-grid section">
			<div class="hero-copy">
				<p class="kicker">About</p>
				<h1>ILAI Academy is the public expression of a deeper professional question: how should serious people use AI well?</h1>
				<p class="lead">
					Dr. MTD Lakshan is a Consultant ENT and Head &amp; Neck Surgeon, Director and Head of the
					Research and Education Foundation at Nawaloka Hospitals, Honorary Senior Lecturer in Medical
					Education at the University of Kelaniya, and founder of ILAI Academy.
				</p>
				<p class="body-copy">
					His work sits at the intersection of clinical care, medical education, institutional development,
					and AI-enabled thinking. Rather than treating AI as a novelty, he approaches it as a force that
					must be understood pedagogically, ethically, and operationally.
				</p>
			</div>

			<aside class="card profile-card">
				<img src="/images/about/teaching.jpg" alt="Dr. MTD Lakshan teaching about AI in a lecture setting" class="profile-image teaching-image" />
				<p class="profile-caption">Dr. MTD Lakshan teaching about AI in a clinical and educational setting.</p>
				<ul class="profile-list">
					<li>Clinical practice in ENT and head &amp; neck surgery</li>
					<li>Medical education, faculty development, and public speaking</li>
					<li>Institutional AI policy, governance, and implementation work</li>
				</ul>
			</aside>
		</section>

		<section class="grid two-up section">
			<article class="card panel">
				<p class="kicker">Why ILAI exists</p>
				<h2>A credible public home for serious work on AI in medicine and education.</h2>
				<p>
					ILAI Academy was created to provide a coherent space for writing, teaching, speaking, and
					collaboration around AI in medicine, medical education, and institutional life.
				</p>
				<p>
					The emphasis is on first principles, responsible adoption, and preserving the human core of
					learning, judgement, and care.
				</p>
			</article>

			<article class="card panel">
				<p class="kicker">Current focus</p>
				<h2>The work is practical, educational, and institutional.</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>AI in medical education and faculty development</li>
					<li>AI literacy for clinicians and healthcare leaders</li>
					<li>Institutional policy, governance, and implementation</li>
					<li>Writing and speaking on learning, judgement, and responsible AI use</li>
				</ul>
			</article>
		</section>
	</main>

	<SiteFooter />
</Layout>

<style>
	.page {
		padding: 3.5rem 0 2rem;
	}

	.section {
		padding-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.hero-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(320px, 0.8fr);
		gap: 2rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.hero-copy {
		padding-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	.profile-card,
	.panel {
		padding: 1.75rem;
	}

	.profile-card {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 253, 249, 0.92), rgba(247, 242, 235, 0.82));
	}

	.profile-image {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 5 / 6;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		border-radius: 18px;
	}

	.teaching-image {
		aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
		object-position: center center;
	}

	.profile-caption {
		margin: 1rem 0 0;
		font-size: 0.98rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--text);
	}

	.profile-list {
		margin: 1rem 0 0;
		padding-left: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.kicker {
		color: var(--brand-2);
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
		line-height: 1.04;
		letter-spacing: -0.045em;
		margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
		max-width: 14ch;
	}

	h2 {
		margin: 0.4rem 0 0.8rem;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.lead,
	.body-copy,
	p,
	li {
		color: var(--muted);
		line-height: 1.85;
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.grid {
		display: grid;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.two-up {
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
	}

	ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.hero-grid,
		.two-up {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		h1 {
			max-width: unset;
		}
	}
</style>
